", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n38371", "headword_ar": "مَرَّةٌ", "root": "mr", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A time; one time;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[in the sense of the French"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fois;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taArapN", "text_ar": "تَارَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Msb:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "one action; a single action"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "act;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mar~N", "text_ar": "مَرٌّ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (M, K: [but see what follows:]) ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a bout; an instance; a case;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a single temporary offection"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "attack; a fit;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as, for instance, of hunger, thirst, disease, and the like:] pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mar~aAtN", "text_ar": "مَرَّاتٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, Msb) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "miraArN", "text_ar": "مِرَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, A, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mirarN", "text_ar": "مِرَرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mar~N", "text_ar": "مَرٌّ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or rather this is a coll. gen. n. of which"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mar~apN", "text_ar": "مَرَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is the n. un.] and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muruwrN", "text_ar": "مُرُورٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (M, K;) the last on the authority of Aboo-'Alee, and occurring in the following verse of Aboo-Dhu-eyb:"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "tanak~arota baEodiY A^amo A^aSaAbaka HaAdivN\n                     \n                     \n                        mino Ald~ahori A^amo mar~ato Ealayoka muruwru"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Hast thou become altered since I saw thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "hath an accident of fortune befallen thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "have vicissitudes come upon thee?"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] but Es-Sukkaree holds that"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mrwr", "text_ar": "مرور"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is an inf. n.; and IJ says, I do not think this improbable, and that the verb is made fem. because the inf. n. implies muchness and genus. (M.) You say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faEalotuhu mar~apF", "text_ar": "فَعَلْتُهُ مَرَّةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I did it once"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], (A, Msb,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mar~aAtK", "text_ar": "مَرَّاتٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "miraArFA", "text_ar": "مِرَارًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "several times"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.) [And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biA@lomar~api", "text_ar": "بِا@لْمَرَّةِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "At once."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laqiyahu *aAta mar~apK", "text_ar": "لَقِيَهُ ذَاتَ مَرَّةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He met him once"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: only used adverbially: (M, K:) so says Sb. (M.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laqiyahu *aAta AlmiraAri", "text_ar": "لَقِيَهُ ذَاتَ المِرَارِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He met him many times:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:) [or this has a different signification; for] you say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fulaAnN yaSonaEu *`lika AlA^amora *aAta AlmiraAri", "text_ar": "فُلَانٌ يَصْنَعُ ذٰلِكَ الاَمْرَ ذَاتَ المِرَارِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one does that thing sometimes,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and sometimes he leaves it undone. (ISk, S.) Also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jiy^otuhu mar~FA A^awo mar~ayoni", "text_ar": "جِيْتُهُ مَرًّا اَوْ مَرَّيْنِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", i. e.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mar~apF A^awo mar~atayoni", "text_ar": "مَرَّةً اَوْ مَرَّتَيْنِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I came to him once"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "twice"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (M, K.)"}], "source_refs": ["Msb", "A", "S", "M", "K"]}, {"entry_id": "n3691", "headword_ar": "مَرَّةٌ", "root": "tA^r", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": (Msb, K:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a time, whether long or short;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HiynN", "text_ar": "حِينٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (IAar:) sometimes, however, it is pronounced"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taA^orapN", "text_ar": "تَاْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Msb:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tiy^arN", "text_ar": "تِيَرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tiy^aArN", "text_ar": "تِيَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Msb:) these are pls. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taA^orapN", "text_ar": "تَاْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; but the pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taArapN", "text_ar": "تَارَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "without"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "'", "text_ar": "ء"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taAraAtN", "text_ar": "تَارَاتٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tiyarN", "text_ar": "تِيَرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tyr", "text_ar": "تير"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and K and K in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "twr", "text_ar": "تور"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",) and"}